reviewText: Total Dissappointment. This is a dubbed Hindi version of an old Gujarati movie titled "Sati Midalsa". I liked the originally movie, but was completely disappointed with this dubbed version of the movie. The songs were totally out of sych with the original movie. Im totally sore that I had spent that price on this movie. If you want to watch this story, I suggest you try to find Sati Midalsa and watch it with subtitles. The original songs are far better.
